WEBVTT

00:00:42.240 --> 00:00:43.000
Well?

00:00:43.439 --> 00:00:44.679
What can you do to me?

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:47.159
We can't do anything to you.

00:00:53.560 --> 00:00:54.759
But the law can.

00:00:59.119 --> 00:00:59.920
Yi Xin.

00:01:00.439 --> 00:01:01.479
Pleasure working with you.

00:01:05.920 --> 00:01:06.599
Yi Xin.

00:01:06.959 --> 00:01:07.920
You witch.

00:01:08.159 --> 00:01:09.159
How dare you lie to me.

00:01:19.719 --> 00:01:20.640
Jiang Nanshuo.

00:01:21.799 --> 00:01:23.480
I've finally waited for this day.

00:01:24.879 --> 00:01:27.680
I want to watch your ugly heart...

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:29.879
...shatter into pieces...

00:01:31.239 --> 00:01:32.400
...and rot into mud.

00:01:36.959 --> 00:01:38.480
You joined forces to set me up.

00:01:38.680 --> 00:01:39.599
Just you wait.

00:01:39.640 --> 00:01:41.120
Someone won't let anything happen to me.

00:01:42.719 --> 00:01:43.640
Sorry.

00:01:43.879 --> 00:01:46.680
The subscriber you dialed is not answering.

00:01:48.159 --> 00:01:49.079
Sorry.

00:01:49.719 --> 00:01:50.519
Jiang Nanshuo.

00:01:50.680 --> 00:01:52.239
Do you think they can still get away with it?

00:01:52.239 --> 00:01:53.640
Please try again later.

00:01:53.959 --> 00:01:54.879
Sorry.

00:01:55.120 --> 00:01:57.920
The subscriber you dialed is not answering.

00:01:58.040 --> 00:01:59.159
Please try again later.

00:02:06.079 --> 00:02:06.680
Are you okay?

00:02:10.439 --> 00:02:11.159
I'm fine.

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:14.039
In fact...

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:18.759
I think that felt so good.

00:02:20.639 --> 00:02:21.240
Hei Ba.

00:02:22.639 --> 00:02:23.879
Was I cool just now?

00:02:24.639 --> 00:02:25.360
You were alright.

00:02:28.759 --> 00:02:29.800
Right?

00:02:30.319 --> 00:02:32.639
Once Sister Yi Xin finds all the evidence...

00:02:33.319 --> 00:02:34.120
...all of this...

00:02:34.439 --> 00:02:36.080
...will be over, right?

00:02:36.439 --> 00:02:37.599
All of this.

00:02:40.919 --> 00:02:41.479
Yi Xin.

00:02:43.159 --> 00:02:43.960
Yi Xin is in danger.

00:02:57.280 --> 00:02:58.680
Are you looking for this?

00:03:14.360 --> 00:03:15.159
It's fake.

00:03:17.319 --> 00:03:18.039
Where is the USB drive?

00:03:18.680 --> 00:03:19.639
The USB drive?

00:03:20.680 --> 00:03:22.400
It's gone where it belongs.

00:03:24.159 --> 00:03:25.639
You thought getting that USB drive...

00:03:26.520 --> 00:03:27.719
...would let you threaten me?

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:29.319
Threaten?

00:03:30.520 --> 00:03:31.560
You're wrong.

00:03:32.039 --> 00:03:33.800
I never intended to threaten you.

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:37.479
From the moment I came to your side...

00:03:38.159 --> 00:03:39.759
...I've had only one goal.

00:03:40.520 --> 00:03:41.639
To destroy you.

00:03:43.759 --> 00:03:44.639
Destroy me?

00:03:45.479 --> 00:03:46.719
You think you can?

00:03:46.919 --> 00:03:47.639
Yes.

00:03:48.159 --> 00:03:49.120
Remember this.

00:03:50.159 --> 00:03:51.639
The one who destroyed you with her own hands...

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:54.000
...is the Long Weiwei from ten years ago...

00:03:55.400 --> 00:03:57.240
...and the Yi Xin of ten years later.

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:08.639
Weiwei.

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:12.199
Witch.

00:04:22.800 --> 00:04:23.600
President Sun.

00:04:24.480 --> 00:04:26.079
Why haven't you been answering my calls?

00:04:26.839 --> 00:04:27.639
Jiang Nanshuo.

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:29.399
For the sake of our years of cooperation...

00:04:29.399 --> 00:04:30.519
...I'll give you a heads-up.

00:04:30.839 --> 00:04:32.160
Your dirty dealings have been exposed.

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:33.680
While there's still time...

00:04:34.079 --> 00:04:35.000
...hurry up and run.

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:36.319
President Sun.

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:37.079
You...

00:04:37.079 --> 00:04:38.000
What does this mean?

00:04:38.399 --> 00:04:39.680
I've already thought of a way.

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:40.560
Where are you right now?

00:04:40.639 --> 00:04:41.839
None of your business.

00:04:42.199 --> 00:04:43.399
You're on your own.

00:04:43.519 --> 00:04:44.319
P-President Sun.

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:45.279
President Sun!

00:04:49.639 --> 00:04:50.040
Run.

00:04:51.199 --> 00:04:52.079
Only by running...

00:04:52.759 --> 00:04:54.000
...can I have a chance to start over.

00:05:10.680 --> 00:05:11.600
What are you laughing at?

00:05:11.920 --> 00:05:13.879
You only think of running now?

00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:16.639
It's too late.

00:05:17.839 --> 00:05:18.959
What do you mean?

00:05:19.519 --> 00:05:20.680
All of your money...

00:05:21.279 --> 00:05:22.399
...is in my hands.

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:24.160
Without money,

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:25.000
you...

00:05:25.879 --> 00:05:27.959
...are just a stray dog.

00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:29.800
Give my money back to me!

00:05:35.279 --> 00:05:35.959
I beg you.

00:05:36.759 --> 00:05:38.000
Give my money back to me.

00:05:42.519 --> 00:05:43.639
Whatever grudges we have...

00:05:44.040 --> 00:05:45.079
...I can kneel down...

00:05:45.560 --> 00:05:46.600
...and confess to you.

00:05:47.279 --> 00:05:48.000
Please.

00:05:48.639 --> 00:05:49.480
Give me a way out.

00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:51.800
Just one way.

00:05:51.959 --> 00:05:52.839
Just one.

00:06:11.600 --> 00:06:12.680
It's just kneeling.

00:06:13.879 --> 00:06:15.040
Is that so impressive?

00:06:18.279 --> 00:06:18.680
Look.

00:06:19.959 --> 00:06:21.040
I knelt down too.

00:06:22.439 --> 00:06:23.560
Is it useful?

00:06:24.639 --> 00:06:25.720
Jiang Nanshuo.

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:28.240
All your money has been frozen by judicial authorities.

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:30.759
Guess...

00:06:31.480 --> 00:06:33.279
...who provided...

00:06:34.199 --> 00:06:36.240
...the most critical evidence?

00:06:45.279 --> 00:06:46.360
You bitch!

00:06:51.279 --> 00:06:52.240
You want to die?

00:06:52.600 --> 00:06:53.600
I'll grant your wish!

00:06:53.759 --> 00:06:55.120
You forced me to do this!

00:06:58.920 --> 00:07:00.160
Ten years ago...

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:02.680
...when Long Weiwei was driven to death by you...

00:07:03.040 --> 00:07:04.160
...she could only be at your mercy.

00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:05.800
Nowadays...

00:07:06.439 --> 00:07:08.639
...I can take you down with me.

00:07:09.240 --> 00:07:09.639
I...

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:11.759
...will die a worthy death.

00:07:12.959 --> 00:07:13.519
Lang Jiu...

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:15.319
Lang Jiu said it long ago.

00:07:15.959 --> 00:07:17.079
He said there was something wrong with you.

00:07:17.279 --> 00:07:18.160
But I didn't believe him.

00:07:20.120 --> 00:07:20.759
Weiwei...

00:07:21.079 --> 00:07:22.079
Weiwei, you're back.

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:23.720
Let's go together...

00:07:23.879 --> 00:07:25.319
...let's leave here together, okay?

00:07:27.759 --> 00:07:29.319
Let's die together.

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:42.959
So that's how it is.

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:45.800
What a great scheme.

00:07:46.519 --> 00:07:47.680
What a pity.

00:07:48.240 --> 00:07:49.680
Even if I'm really finished...

00:07:50.920 --> 00:07:52.879
...I won't let you off easy.

00:08:09.319 --> 00:08:10.839
You think bringing me down...

00:08:10.839 --> 00:08:11.759
...will make you happy?

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:13.720
I am Jiang Nanshuo!

00:08:14.480 --> 00:08:16.160
There's nothing in this life I haven't enjoyed.

00:08:16.759 --> 00:08:17.759
I have no regrets.

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:19.800
Such a beautiful scene...

00:08:20.399 --> 00:08:21.920
...I watch it every day.

00:08:22.199 --> 00:08:23.120
Because torturing you...

00:08:24.879 --> 00:08:26.120
...gives me such a thrill.

00:08:28.399 --> 00:08:29.000
What?

00:08:29.759 --> 00:08:30.920
Can't take it anymore?

00:08:31.399 --> 00:08:32.559
This kind of pain...

00:08:33.240 --> 00:08:35.080
...you will never be able to forget.

00:08:47.200 --> 00:08:48.519
The evidence is irrefutable.

00:08:49.240 --> 00:08:50.799
Your crime of rape back then...

00:08:51.639 --> 00:08:54.039
...will certainly receive its due punishment.